{"tha-ap254:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap254:0.2":"Thomakavagga ","tha-ap254:0.3":"Ekasanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap254:1.1":"“Vijahitva devavannam, ","tha-ap254:1.2":"sabhariyo idhagamim; ","tha-ap254:1.3":"Adhikaram kattukamo, ","tha-ap254:1.4":"buddhasetthassa sasane. ","tha-ap254:2.1":"Devalo nama namena, ","tha-ap254:2.2":"padumuttarasavako; ","tha-ap254:2.3":"Tassa bhikkha maya dinna, ","tha-ap254:2.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap254:3.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap254:3.2":"yam kammamakarim tada; ","tha-ap254:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap254:3.4":"pindapatassidam phalam. ","tha-ap254:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap254:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap254:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap254:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekasanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap254:6.1":"Ekasanadayakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}